### 🔹 Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/timesheet

### =====================================================================================
### 👥 EMPLOYEES
### =====================================================================================

### ➕ Criar novo colaborador
POST {{baseUrl}}/Employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ID": "E005",
  "name": "Miguel Terrivel",
  "email": "miguel.terrivel@innovatech.com"
}

###

### 📋 Listar todos os colaboradores
GET {{baseUrl}}/Employees

###

### 🔍 Obter colaborador específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/Employees('E001')

###

### 🗑️ Eliminar colaborador
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/Employees('E003')


